data.description: Great Location With NO HOA or CDD! This beautiful MOVE-IN Ready House has 1673 Sqft. 4 Bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 car garage. The kitchen has lots of storage and recently updated fridge, Microwave and Dishwasher, the Washer and dryer are also fairly new. The Roof is ONLY 3 Month old, The A/C is the original but was recently repaired and works great! The house has beautiful and well taken care wood floors throughout the main living areas and tile and carpet on the rest of the house. Come and see the beautiful BIG Back yard, big enough to add a pool or just to enjoy as it is and gather with family and friends. Conveniently located close to Historic Downtown Sebring, Harder Hall Resort Club, Sebring Municipal Golf Course, shopping, and restaurants. Max Long Recreational Complex and Highlands County Family YMCA are only a few minutes away too.
